re>       </div>                        <div class="modal js-modal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/img/TS-48091_CTV_Mapping_Project_-_Poker_Games_CTV_Blast_Teaser-1628837534056_tcm1488-527978.jpg" width="600" height="338" alt="TS-48091_CTV_Mapping_Project_-_Poker_Games_CTV_Blast_Teaser-1628837534056_tcm1488-527978" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div> </div>                 <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component None None">     <div class="text"> <p>The new BLAST Sit &amp; Go is an exciting Sit &amp; Go game where you could win big! 3 players are in for a fun surprise as they compete for a randomly drawn prize pool.Every time you play a BLAST Sit and Go you could be playing for a prize pool <strong>of up to 10,000 times your buy-in!</strong></p><p>The higher the prize pool multiplier – the more chips you get, and the longer the blind levels.</p></div> </div></div>                 <div class="progressive-item">         <div class="progressive-item-component">              <div class="progressive-number-component false">     <div class="number">1</div> </div>       <div class="grid-component">         <div class="column-container two-columns-50 landscape-two inverted">             <div class="column left">                            <div class="image-component img-100">       <div class="image-container js-modal-open modal-enabled">                               <picture>                  <img src="/img/1-CTV_Mapping_Project-Poker_Games_screenshots-Blast-01-Here_E2_80_99s_how_it_works-TS-48091-1662709350683_tcm1488-566633.jpg" width="1200" height="675" alt="1" loading="lazy">     </picture>       </div>                        <div class="modal js-modal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/img/1-CTV_Mapping_Project-Poker_Games_screenshots-Blast-01-Here_E2_80_99s_how_it_works-TS-48091-1662709350683_tcm1488-566633.jpg" width="1200" height="675" alt="1" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div>              </div>             <div class="column right">                         <div class="title-component">     <h2 class="h2 text-left">         Here’s how it works     </h2> </div>                              <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><div contentexportchild="richtext"><p>BLAST is a 3-handed, Super-turbo Texas Hold’em Sit &amp; Go. To add to the suspense, the prize pool of each BLAST Sit &amp; Go remains a mystery until the game begins. It is determined based on a draw that takes place at the beginning of each BLAST tournament and varies between two and 10,000 times the buy-in.</p> <p>The blind structure and prize pool distribution of each BLAST Sit &amp; Go is determined according to the multiplier that was assigned to the BLAST Sit &amp; Go.</p> <p>When you register for a BLAST Sit &amp; Go, you’ll be automatically placed in a BLAST Sit &amp; Go with 2 other players. As soon as 3 players have registered, a draw takes place in order to determine the prize pool.</p> </div></div> </div>                                             </div>         </div>     </div> </div> </div>                 <div class="progressive-item">         <div class="progressive-item-component">              <